@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="atz-card p-4 legal-page">
    <h1 class="atz-section-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">1. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We collect clinic profile data, user account details, and clinical operational records that your staff enter into the application (patients, appointments, billing, etc.).</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">2. How we use information</h2>
    <p>Data is used to operate the service, authenticate users, provide support, send transactional emails (password reset, trial reminders), and maintain security audit logs.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">3. Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell patient data. Infrastructure providers (hosting, email, payment processing) may process data solely to deliver the service under contractual safeguards.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">4. Retention</h2>
    <p>Data is retained while your subscription is active. Clinic administrators may export data from Admin → Data Privacy. Deletion requests remove tenant data from our primary database.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>Where applicable, you may request access, correction, export, or deletion of personal data. Use the in-app data export tool or contact your clinic administrator.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">6. Security</h2>
    <p>We apply tenant isolation, encrypted transport (HTTPS), access controls, and audit logging. No system is 100% secure — report concerns promptly.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy requests: contact your clinic administrator or system vendor.</p>
</div>
